Api is code which we get represetation of the database of current state not the actual state this is called restapi.

FastApi : a python framework to build apis.
fast, async programming. python 3.6+ 
how it's better: its speed orientantion, can validate the datatypes, json, oauth and Open api.
much faster to build an api, production ready. interactive and automatic documention.


